Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到是阿斯拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.23,0:02:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從在自由試車時來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車型看來和花環沒多大分別
