Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.27,0:02:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心 今次我會避開他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.78,0:03:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好他跟那個笨蛋一眼就能看出差別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他成了大家注目的焦點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.82,0:03:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他在明天的決賽裡會更令人驚訝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最優先的是收集資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.37,0:03:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保留實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.49,0:03:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.29,0:03:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.95,0:03:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和那部跑車比賽 真是榮幸呢
