Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡爾.里胥特.馮.蘭德爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.43,0:03:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑出1分36秒268
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.87,0:03:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進佔第二位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.65,0:03:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺有精神的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.66,0:03:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 因為我已了無牽掛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.81,0:03:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6號車 AOI ZIP的菲爾.弗利茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.37,0:03:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始預賽計時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.29,0:04:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一心一意進行比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管面對的是甚麼樣的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.11,0:04:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只有那樣才能取勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.66,0:04:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會取得冠軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.83,0:04:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.96,0:04:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為自己是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.32,0:04:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口出狂言 竟敢說會取得冠軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.95,0:04:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真是 你一把年紀幹甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.47,0:04:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 黃毛小子卻大言不慚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的以為能贏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你和那部「老爺車」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是還有可能會優勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.57,0:04:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺車？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那傢伙也變化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.95,0:04:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小看阿斯拉會自食惡果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.80,0:04:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會輸給你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.95,0:04:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請你先去參加預賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.22,0:05:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就快結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.52,0:05:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是說笑的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話那麼大膽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.54,0:05:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.52,0:05:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有那種新的轉彎技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天也會使用新型推進器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒見到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前隼人你在賽車場上的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.60,0:05:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AOI ZIP菲爾.弗利茲的時間是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.33,0:05:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1分34秒353
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.47,0:05:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最快的圈速紀錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.24,0:05:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓他看明天才是真正的比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.70,0:05:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見起步絕妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣過了古利特和布魯斯賀魯玆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.83,0:06:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在過第一個彎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.52,0:06:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是風見久違了的超凡技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.32,0:06:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在混戰裡亦超過了哈利  在一瞬間升上第五位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.48,0:06:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!所以我才討厭那部車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了三輛車嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 風見先生了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.18,0:06:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.92,0:06:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.74,0:06:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種混戰對隼人有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.90,0:06:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽的發展真是出人意表
