Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.21,0:06:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見一瞬間升上第三位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.15,0:06:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追著遙遙領先的 AL-ZARD軍團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.42,0:07:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人只是追上來你就「心慌」了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「心慌」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.33,0:07:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候會說這麼庸俗的話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.59,0:07:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.21,0:07:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人說他會贏那部AL-ZARD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.17,0:07:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.82,0:07:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實只有隼人才會有這樣的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果隼人真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.01,0:07:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果贏了他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.04,0:07:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼他們的所做就會變得毫無意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.13,0:07:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也許就達到目的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.32,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們車手間的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.27,0:07:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我佩服你的決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.08,0:07:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也不想輕易輸給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.96,0:07:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是加賀 是菲爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.98,0:08:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升壓渦開動 即將到達引擎臨界點 倒數開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 注意時間和小心壓力過大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.54,0:08:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5秒後到達第一次臨界點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.44,0:08:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.42,0:08:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動!螺旋升壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.47,0:08:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.26,0:08:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害的阿斯拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可以說是二段推進器吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它狂追用推進器加速的 AL-ZARD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.12,0:08:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害!像噴射機一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.04,0:08:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儲存平常升壓的一定時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.67,0:08:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行爆炸性的第二次加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個簡單卻有效的對策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.78,0:09:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝擊來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.33,0:09:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.55,0:09:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.73,0:09:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速!應該還可以加速的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.73,0:09:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 再加速的話輪胎會..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.59,0:09:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趁現在換胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.07,0:09:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見終於超越加賀升上第二位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.32,0:09:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫近開幕以來除了退出就從未讓出冠軍寶座的弗利茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.41,0:09:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見過去曾多次創造奇跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.60,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看起來他去年似乎已江郎才盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在他風采依然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.67,0:09:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他穩步迫近菲爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.64,0:09:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不怕會相撞嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.05,0:10:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作 菲爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.90,0:10:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算再次變回失敗者嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.26,0:10:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本小子鬥志激昂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.09,0:10:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.57,0:10:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你沒妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.37,0:10:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天就能和隼人來一場有趣的比賽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有趣的必敗的比賽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.78,0:10:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明知故問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決...決...決...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決決決?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.80,0:10:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.08,0:10:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓力衝擊對那傢伙無效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有何打算?隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.69,0:10:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有7圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.14,0:11:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法拋離他也沒關係 能壓制他就會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.48,0:11:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.32,0:11:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉 準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.33,0:11:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 追上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.02,0:11:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋升壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.61,0:11:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中轉彎嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.05,0:12:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟發生甚麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.54,0:12:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安哈特和弗利茲相撞 一起退出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.91,0:12:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見先生帥呆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.96,0:12:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝過終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.61,0:12:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠軍是菅生的風見隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.62,0:12:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他低迷了很久了 今季是第一次優勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.58,0:13:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天馬」現在高舉雙手 他再次復活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.41,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可愛...你這傢伙真是不可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.01,0:13:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可愛也沒所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也很久沒勝出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到我會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.85,0:13:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.91,0:13:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己體內有多少潛力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實連自己也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.42,0:13:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你放棄嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.06,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連試試挑戰都沒有就放棄了嗎
