Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.12,0:14:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs31\bord0\pos(318,374)}第8戰     英國杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.12,0:14:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs31\bord0\pos(318,440)}伯斯特橋機場賽車場
