Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.70,0:15:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\fs31\bord0\pos(318,440)}香港市區賽車場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己應該也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.31,0:16:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果繼續這樣 你的身體會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.54,0:16:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能半途而廢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.84,0:16:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.66,0:16:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 你回來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.18,0:16:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為下星期便舉行日本杯車賽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.75,0:16:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.53,0:16:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你最近看來也沒回公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.29,0:17:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在調查嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真是辛苦極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不單是尾巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.40,0:17:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連足跡也巧妙地藏起來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒尾巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.68,0:17:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也真是不容易死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.79,0:17:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今日是來向我爸爸辯解的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是去說明戰況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.05,0:17:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們還有機會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.23,0:17:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若下一站輸給風見隼人就完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.59,0:17:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時 你就會為當初的優勝保證負責任吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.49,0:17:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.35,0:17:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.49,0:18:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs31\bord0\pos(322,372)}第11戰   日本杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.49,0:18:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs31\bord0\pos(318,440)}灣岸特製賽車場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.86,0:18:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃電霹靂車世界錦標賽也只剩下兩站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.32,0:18:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮聳立著的「彩虹橋」在秋色中倒映在水面上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.54,0:18:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本站的戰場就是建在灣岸地區的特製賽車場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.79,0:18:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽道全長29.167公里 總共15圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.17,0:18:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如這條橋的名稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.24,0:18:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟誰會走過彩虹成為冠軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.08,0:18:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠軍爭奪戰也達到了高潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.35,0:18:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蘭披治現在備受注目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積分表上 從第六站德國起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.29,0:18:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉著驚人的「五連勝」得到53分的風見隼人現在領先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.86,0:18:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑著震撼的出道賽\N而令世上閃電霹靂車迷驚訝的弗利茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.66,0:18:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也以46分佔著第二位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.45,0:18:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但比賽的形勢最近急轉直下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.39,0:18:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要反敗為勝會很困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.18,0:18:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡爾.里胥特.馮.蘭德爾有38分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑奇.古德利安有36分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.87,0:19:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Union Savior有車手中途加入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.02,0:19:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.35,0:19:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他在試車時創造了很快的時間記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.06,0:19:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有點古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.79,0:19:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就讓我介紹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.86,0:19:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們Union Savior旗下參賽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.88,0:19:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.55,0:19:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是新條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.56,0:19:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我想把他當作「神秘車手」介紹給大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你壞了我大事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那怎麼稱得上神秘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.80,0:19:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 他沒必要隱瞞身份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他和你那時候不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.01,0:19:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這是舒馬赫以來Union Savior的傳統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我!艾迪利.布魯斯賀魯玆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今日一定要教訓他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.11,0:20:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 在這裡能見到你 我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.54,0:20:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.44,0:20:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能讓我看到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.69,0:20:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以往不同的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會打敗你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.34,0:20:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.02,0:20:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也叫甚麼神秘車手嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.06,0:21:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.65,0:21:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有何貴幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別那麼冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.85,0:21:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直就想找機會和你詳談一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒話跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.68,0:21:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒揭露你的秘密是為了今日子小姐和加賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.90,0:21:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有菲爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.48,0:21:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了菲爾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.01,0:21:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓他看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.65,0:21:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所做的毫無意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.83,0:21:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓他知道相信自己的力量去比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會成為真正的勝利者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.72,0:22:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.10,0:22:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那口吻也和令尊一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.66,0:22:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說令尊對自己的信念也是很頑固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.57,0:22:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.18,0:22:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥以前曾和令尊一起工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.58,0:22:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一起開發阿斯拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.72,0:22:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說我哥哥和令尊遇上時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.20,0:22:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊跟我哥哥說他\N正著手開發前所未有的閃電霹靂車跑車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.27,0:22:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥非常欽佩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.88,0:22:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他馬上作為令尊的下屬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.74,0:22:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起合作開發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.81,0:22:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.01,0:23:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也認識克蕾雅小姐和修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.89,0:23:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是他們尚未加入時候的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.23,0:23:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時還是一籌莫展毫無理念的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.40,0:23:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失陪一會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.20,0:23:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人和跑車的融合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.55,0:23:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑車的理想新構造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.49,0:23:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在令尊這個偉大的目標面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.95,0:23:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開發多次都還是停滯不前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.03,0:23:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 我哥哥有一個提議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.13,0:23:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道是甚麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.97,0:23:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是以生化電腦為媒體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.95,0:23:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人的腦部一體化的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.17,0:23:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到同僚們的贊成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.21,0:23:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那構思曾被著手開發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.87,0:23:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只是令尊堅持己見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.49,0:23:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接受這提議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.48,0:23:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說那是錯誤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.34,0:24:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我哥哥的提議通過的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.50,0:24:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的AL-ZARD或許就是阿斯拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.79,0:24:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.23,0:24:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我哥哥的理論哪裡有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.04,0:24:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這系統會令人為錯誤消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.80,0:24:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保障車手的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.77,0:24:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本就是令尊的目標啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.96,0:24:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然是錯誤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.75,0:24:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的目標 人和跑車的融合不是那種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.49,0:24:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科技進步 人的理念也會改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.49,0:24:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AL-ZARD成為新時代的跑車有何不妥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.28,0:24:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 人們追求它的高速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.11,0:24:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對科技的進步報以喝采聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.32,0:24:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃電霹靂車應該就是那樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.08,0:24:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.26,0:24:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃電霹靂車不是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:55.61,0:24:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使跑車怎樣進化也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.58,0:25:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比賽的始終是我們車手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.43,0:25:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.06,0:25:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是造出能協助我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.48,0:25:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們一起並肩作戰的跑車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.30,0:25:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰對誰錯早晚會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.31,0:25:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由人們來決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.94,0:25:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會證明給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.95,0:25:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了和令尊分道揚鑣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.60,0:25:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為喝采聲賭上一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.78,0:25:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而死不瞑目的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.41,0:25:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做甚麼 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.84,0:25:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.24,0:25:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菅生小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.65,0:25:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:42.95,0:25:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見先生有留話給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.74,0:25:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說有點疲倦 先回去休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:49.68,0:25:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣嗎
